    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Steam heating systems that include vacuum pumps that separate air from condensation in the return main of the system, maintaining the pressure at a constant level and accelerating the circulation of steam.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000014901/Hamlin, Forms and Functions of 20th Century Architecture (1952)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Usese para sistemas de calefacción de vapor que incluyen bombas de vacío que separan el aire de la condensación en el retorno principal del sistema, manteniendo la presión a un nivel constante y acelerando la circulación del vapor.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wordt gebruikt voor stoomverwarmingssystemen die vacuumpompen bevatten om lucht van condenswater te scheiden in de retourhoofdleidingen van het systeem, waardoor de druk op een constant niveau blijft en de stoomcirculatie wordt versneld.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>利用真空幫浦，在回流總管中分離空氣與凝結水的蒸汽加熱系統，維持一定的壓力，加速蒸氣循環。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000250/AS-Academia Sinica</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
      </Descriptive_Note>
    </Descriptive_Notes>
